title: Voxel count (LM)
description: Number of voxels in the binary labelmap representation of the segment.

title: Volume (LM)
description: Volume of the segment computed from binary labelmap representation.

title: Volume (LM)
description: Volume of the segment computed from binary labelmap representation.

title: Voxel count (SV)
description: Number of voxels. Computed from region of the binary labelmap representation of the segment that overlaps with the input scalar volume.

title: Volume (SV)
description: Volume of the region of the binary labelmap representation that overlaps with the input scalar volume.

title: Volume (SV)
description: Volume of the region of the binary labelmap representation that overlaps with the input scalar volume.

title: Minimum
description: Minimum input scalar volume voxel value within the segment.

title: Maximum
description: Maximum input scalar volume voxel value within the segment.

title: Mean
description: Mean input scalar volume voxel value within the segment.

title: Median
description: Median input scalar volume voxel value within the segment.

title: Standard Deviation
description: Standard deviation of input scalar volume voxel values within the segment.

title: Surface area
description: Surface area computed from closed surface representation.

title: Volume (CS)
description: Volume computed from closed surface representation.

title: Volume (CS)
description: Volume computed from closed surface representation.
